msgid "# Decode Context Parallel (DCP)"
msgstr "# 解码上下文并行（DCP）"

msgid ""
"Decode Context Parallel shards the KV cache along the sequence dimension "
"across devices in a Tensor Parallel (TP) group. It eliminates redundant "
"KV-cache storage without adding devices to the process world."
msgstr ""
"解码上下文并行在张量并行（TP）组内沿序列维度将 KV 缓存分片到不同设备，"
"无需增加进程组设备数量即可消除重复的 KV 缓存存储。"

